  "texts": [
    "Further advancements can be made by augmenting the model with memory, additional tools, and sophisticated prompting schemes.These systems, often referred to as language agents, have garnered significant research attention recently.",
    "For a comprehensive overview, one may refer to [127,128].",
    "In this section, we aim to underscore the pivotal role of such systems in enhancing the capabilities of raw language models, particularly in terms of their generalization.",
    "In-context learningIn-context learning [129], as exemplified by techniques such as chain-of-thought prompting, offers means to instill desired biases into models without explicit training.",
    "For instance, presenting the model with examples of reasoning in similar tasks can prompt it to employ similar reasoning in its responses [130]."
